title: [Winterchime's Magic Shoppe]
[Winterchime's General Store]
description: Beneath an uneven wooden ceiling, a fused sun and moon wall-hanging hangs on one of the plain wooden walls.  A gold-leafed mistwood cabinet and a Vornavian silk-lined display case sit in opposite corners while a worn rug rests on an unfinished wooden floor.

Beneath a glass-tiled vaulted ceiling, a fused sun and moon wall-hanging hangs on one of the painted white plaster walls.  A gold-leafed mistwood cabinet and a Vornavian silk-lined display case sit in opposite corners while a woven Vornavian silk rug rests on a gold-speckled marble floor.
